Paper: hep-th/9705195

Date: 1997-05-26

Title: Scalar-Tensor Theory of Gravity on $M_4\times Z_{2}$ Geometry

Authors: Akira Kokado, Gaku Konisi, Takesi Saito and Yutaka Tada

Comments: 17 pages, LaTeX, no figures

In the Brans-Dicke(BD) theory on $M_{4}\times Z_{2}$ geometry the geometricalmeaning of the torsion is clarified. The BD theory on $M_{4}\times Z_{2}$ isrederived by taking into account of a new isometry condition.